            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">bot . Gardens 28 [Oct] 53. ¶ Sir William ¶  ¶ Just before leaving Melbourne for my new journey, I observed that our solitary specimen of Cryptostemon ericaeus bears flowers again and I beg therefore t...</supplied>
